citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 10:45am on 23-
JUN-21. The inspector called phone number on file with no answer, left message. The inspector honked horn, knocked on
door with no answer, placed flyer in door. The inspector waited 45 minutes and called again with no answer, left message.
The inspector then left the site.
End Section
